1)Pay special attention to the requeriments documents.
2)Every requeriment is an activity on its own.
3)Enumerate test scenarios (every possible situation, as reasonable as possible).
4)Relate every test scenario to a requeriment.
5)Review.
6)Share with a supervisore.
7)Share with stakeholders.


How to write scenarios?
1) Search for it in google or using AI(should be as adapatable as possible to our producte or services).
2) Manual map.
3)Experience from other similar tested products or services.
